msgstr "8–12 GB VRAM 환경에서 속도와 품질의 최적 균형"

#: ../../ai-agent/configuration.md:95
msgid "Complex analysis, multi-step tool calls"
msgstr "복잡한 분석, 다단계 도구 호출"

#: ../../ai-agent/configuration.md:95
msgid "`qwen3.5:35b`"
msgstr "`qwen3.5:35b`"

#: ../../ai-agent/configuration.md:95
